26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_fuse_gm107.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:34 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "priv.h"
30
31static u32
32gm107_fuse_read(struct nvkm_fuse *fuse, u32 addr)
33{
34 struct nvkm_device *device = fuse->subdev.device;
35 return nvkm_rd32(device, 0x021100 + addr);
36}
37
38static const struct nvkm_fuse_func
39gm107_fuse = {
40 .read = gm107_fuse_read,
41};
42
43int
44gm107_fuse_new(struct nvkm_device *device, int index, struct nvkm_fuse **pfuse)
45{
46 return nvkm_fuse_new_(&gm107_fuse, device, index, pfuse);
47}
